item.title: You Won't Believe What Happens When You Check All Website Pages!
item.description: Introduction Do you ever wonder what happens when you check all of the pages on your website? You may be surprised to learn that checking all of your website pages can have a huge impact on your website’s performance. In this blog post, we’ll discuss the definition of a website page, the benefits of checking website pages, and the reasons why you should check all of your website pages. Definition of Website Page A website page is a single page on a website.
